687
00:48:28,410 --> 00:48:34,750
Rym: My character will on her own say in a way that my teammates can hear.

688
00:48:35,272 --> 00:48:37,530
Rym: There's a sniper by the point.

689
00:48:39,191 --> 00:48:40,778
